version_description: So this is a trickier song out of MCR's discography since it seems to have a lot of blues elements. A lot of improvisation can be done with the chords in this song but I think I was able to pick out the more important chords that structure the song.
Combined and fixed from other submissions.

There were two version already that were okay, but I kept mixing both when playing because they each had something that the other hadn't, so I decided to mash them . I basically copied the existing one, but fixed it up, added and removed some chords, and placed them more correctly according to the lyrics of the song.
These chords are suitable for playing this song acoustically. The song has been slightly edited in order to fit as an acoustic piece.

version_description: Other versions all have parts correct, I've collected all the pieces so that all sections of the song are correct (eg some versions have the prechorus wrong, others have the bridge wrong, etc)
